column5: Does anyone have a quick/simple way to renew the outdoor card/fishing license? I assume it can be done over the internet? If anyone has a quick link or info about it, I would greatly appreciate it.
Second sticky down from the top will get you there. Make sure you follow directions and print off and carry with you.

http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/en/Business...ish/index.htmlVery easy and painless! You can buy your license too! print out the test and if that works you can print it out at home. Happy shopping and fishing!
Thanks a lot, guys. Really appreciate the help.
